\label{Sec:estimator}
Our estimation method is based on approximating the coefficient process $\beta=(\beta_{1},\dots,\beta_{p})^{\top}$ on $[0,T]$ by a linear combination of $K_n$ deterministic polynomial spline basis functions with random weights, where $K_n \to \infty$ as $\Delta_n \to 0$:
