%\end{equation}
which is a static regression model with dependent variable $\Delta_{i}^{n}Y $ and regressors $B_{(i-1)\Delta_{n}}^{(k)}\Delta_{j,i}^{n}X$ for $j=1,\dots,p$ and $k=1,\dots,K_{n}$. When $p$ is fixed, the spline coefficients in $\bm{\gamma}$ can be estimated by OLS.

