Consequently, any time-varying coefficient $\beta$ can be expressed as 
\begin{equation}
\label{Eq:B-spline}
\beta_{t} = \sum_{k=1}^{K_{n}}(\gamma^{(k)})^{\top}B_{t}^{(k)} + e_{t},
